#: app/templates/layout.html:1167
msgid "About Society Speaks"
msgstr "Over Society Speaks"

#: app/templates/layout.html:1170
msgid ""
"A sense-making system that turns disagreement into understanding. We reveal "
"where society agrees, where it divides, and which ideas can bridge the gap."
msgstr ""
"Een zin-vormend systeem dat onenigheid omzet in begrip. We tonen waar de "
"samenleving het eens is, waar ze uiteenloopt en welke ideeën de kloof kunnen"
" overbruggen."

