#: app/templates/terms-and-conditions.html:12
msgid ""
"SocietySpeaks.io (\"we\", \"us\", or \"our\") is operated by William Roberts"
" Coaching and Advisory Ltd, a company incorporated in England (company "
"number 15629688). Our platform provides community discussion and collective "
"intelligence gathering powered by Pol.is technology. The platform is hosted "
