msgid "🕐 Recent"
msgstr "🕐 Recent"

#: app/templates/help/native_system.html:188
msgid "Newest statements first"
msgstr "Nieuwste uitspraken eerst"

#: app/templates/help/native_system.html:196
msgid "Understanding Consensus Analysis"
msgstr "Consensusanalyse begrijpen"

#: app/templates/help/native_system.html:201
msgid ""
"After enough participation (7+ users, 20+ votes), the system analyzes voting"
" patterns to:"
msgstr ""
"Na voldoende deelname (7+ gebruikers, 20+ stemmen) analyseert het systeem "
"stemspreiding om:"

#: app/templates/help/native_system.html:206
msgid "👥 Identify Opinion Groups"
msgstr "👥 Opiniongroepen identificeren"

#: app/templates/help/native_system.html:209
msgid ""
"Users are clustered based on <strong>voting similarity</strong>, not "
"demographics. The system uses PCA (Principal Component Analysis) and "
"Agglomerative Clustering to find natural groupings."
msgstr ""
"Gebruikers worden geclusterd op basis van <strong>stemsimilariteit</strong>,"
" niet op demografische gegevens. Het systeem gebruikt PCA (Principal "
"Component Analysis) en Agglomerative Clustering om natuurlijke groeperingen "
"te vinden."

#: app/templates/help/native_system.html:212
msgid ""
"Example: Group 1 might prioritize environmental concerns, while Group 2 "
"prioritizes economic growth—even if both have mixed political backgrounds."
msgstr ""
"Voorbeeld: Groep 1 kan milieuzorgen voorrang geven, terwijl Groep 2 "
"economische groei voorrang geeft—zelfs als beide gemengde politieke "
"achtergronden hebben."

#: app/templates/help/native_system.html:218
msgid "✅ Detect Consensus Statements"
msgstr "✅ Consensusuitspraken detecteren"

#: app/templates/help/native_system.html:221
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Statements with <strong>≥70%% overall agreement</strong> and <strong>≥60%% "
"in each group</strong> are marked as consensus."
msgstr ""
"Stellingen met <strong>≥70%% algemene instemming</strong> en <strong>≥60%% "
"in elke groep</strong> worden gemarkeerd als consensus."

#: app/templates/help/native_system.html:224
msgid "These represent common ground across different perspectives."
msgstr ""
"Deze vertegenwoordigen gemeenschappelijk terrein tussen verschillende "
"perspectieven."

#: app/templates/help/native_system.html:230
msgid "🌉 Find Bridge Statements"
msgstr "🌉 Vind Brugstellingen"

#: app/templates/help/native_system.html:233
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Statements with <strong>high agreement across all groups</strong> (≥65%% "
"mean, low variance) that unite different perspectives."
msgstr ""
"Stellingen met <strong>hoge instemming in alle groepen</strong> (≥65%% "
"gemiddelde, lage variantie) die verschillende perspectieven verenigen."

#: app/templates/help/native_system.html:236
msgid ""
"These are especially valuable for finding solutions that work for everyone."
msgstr ""
"Deze zijn bijzonder waardevol voor het vinden van oplossingen die voor "
"iedereen werken."

#: app/templates/help/native_system.html:242
msgid "⚡ Highlight Divisive Statements"
msgstr "⚡ Markeer Verdelende Stellingen"

#: app/templates/help/native_system.html:245
msgid ""
"Statements with <strong>close to 50/50</strong> splits (controversy score "
"≥0.7) that reveal deep disagreements."
msgstr ""
"Stellingen met <strong>dicht bij 50/50</strong> verdelingen "
"(controversescores ≥0.7) die diepe meningsverschillen onthullen."

#: app/templates/help/native_system.html:248
msgid "These help identify where dialogue and understanding are most needed."
msgstr ""
"Deze helpen identificeren waar dialoog en begrip het meest nodig zijn."

#: app/templates/help/native_system.html:254
msgid "📊 Visualize with Interactive Charts"
msgstr "📊 Visualiseer met Interactieve Grafieken"

#: app/templates/help/native_system.html:257
msgid ""
"See a <strong>2D scatter plot</strong> where each dot is a participant, "
"colored by opinion group."
msgstr ""
"Zie een <strong>2D-spreidingsdiagram</strong> waarbij elk punt een deelnemer"
" is, gekleurd naar opiniegrroep."

#: app/templates/help/native_system.html:260
msgid ""
"Hover over dots to see details. Closer dots = more similar voting patterns."
msgstr ""
"Beweeg de muisaanwijzer over punten voor details. Dichtere punten = meer "
"vergelijkbare stempatronen."

#: app/templates/help/native_system.html:266
msgid "👀 See It In Action"
msgstr "👀 Zie Het in Actie"

#: app/templates/help/native_system.html:269
msgid ""
"Want to see what all of this looks like? Explore our live demo discussion on"
" climate action and its full consensus analysis."
msgstr ""
"Wil je zien hoe dit er allemaal uitziet? Verken onze live demo-discussie "
"over klimaatmaatregelen en de volledige consensusanalyse."

#: app/templates/help/native_system.html:297
