"💡 Evidence can be marked as <strong>verified</strong>, "
"<strong>pending</strong>, or <strong>disputed</strong> by moderators."
msgstr ""
"💡 Bewijs kan door moderators als <strong>geverifieerd</strong>, <strong>in "
"afwachting</strong> of <strong>betwist</strong> worden gemarkeerd."

