"<strong>User Flagging:</strong> Report spam, offensive content, off-topic "
"posts, or duplicates"
msgstr ""
"<strong>Gebruikersmeldingen:</strong> Rapporteer spam, beledigend materiaal,"
" off-topic berichten of duplicaten"

