msgstr ""
"<code class=\"text-purple-700\">GET /api/partner/webhooks</code> - webhook-"
"eindpunten weergeven"

#: app/templates/partner/api_docs.html:969
msgid ""
"<code class=\"text-purple-700\">POST /api/partner/webhooks</code> - create "
"endpoint and receive signing secret once"
msgstr ""
"<code class=\"text-purple-700\">POST /api/partner/webhooks</code> - eindpunt"
" maken en ondertekeningsgeheim eenmaal ontvangen"

#: app/templates/partner/api_docs.html:970
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"<code class=\"text-purple-700\">PATCH "
"/api/partner/webhooks/{endpoint_id}</code> - pause/resume and update event "
"subscriptions"
msgstr ""
"<code class=\"text-purple-700\">PATCH "
"/api/partner/webhooks/{endpoint_id}</code> - pauzeren/hervatten en "
"gebeurtenisabonnementen bijwerken"

#: app/templates/partner/api_docs.html:971
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"<code class=\"text-purple-700\">POST "
"/api/partner/webhooks/{endpoint_id}/rotate-secret</code> - rotate signing "
"secret"
msgstr ""
"<code class=\"text-purple-700\">POST "
"/api/partner/webhooks/{endpoint_id}/rotate-secret</code> - "
"ondertekeningsgeheim roteren"

#: app/templates/partner/api_docs.html:972
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"<code class=\"text-purple-700\">DELETE "
"/api/partner/webhooks/{endpoint_id}</code> - delete endpoint"
msgstr ""
"<code class=\"text-purple-700\">DELETE "
"/api/partner/webhooks/{endpoint_id}</code> - eindpunt verwijderen"

#: app/templates/partner/api_docs.html:976
msgid "Request headers"
msgstr "Aanvraagheaders"

#: app/templates/partner/api_docs.html:977
msgid "Every webhook delivery includes these headers:"
msgstr "Elke webhook-bezorging bevat deze headers:"

#: app/templates/partner/api_docs.html:982
msgid "Header"
msgstr "Header"

#: app/templates/partner/api_docs.html:987
msgid "Event type, e.g. <code>discussion.created</code>"
msgstr "Gebeurtenistype, bijvoorbeeld <code>discussion.created</code>"

#: app/templates/partner/api_docs.html:988
msgid "Unique event UUID — use for deduplication"
msgstr "Unieke gebeurtenis-UUID — gebruiken voor deduplicatie"

#: app/templates/partner/api_docs.html:989
msgid "Unix seconds (UTC) when the event was sent"
msgstr "Unix-seconden (UTC) wanneer de gebeurtenis werd verzonden"

#: app/templates/partner/api_docs.html:990
msgid "HMAC-SHA256 signature — <strong>always verify this</strong>"
msgstr "HMAC-SHA256-ondertekening — <strong>altijd verifiëren</strong>"

#: app/templates/partner/api_docs.html:997
msgid "Always verify webhook signatures"
msgstr "Webhook-ondertekeningen altijd verifiëren"

#: app/templates/partner/api_docs.html:999
msgid ""
"Without verification, any party that knows your endpoint URL can send forged"
" events. Read the raw body <em>before</em> parsing JSON, then verify the "
"HMAC-SHA256 signature using your signing secret. Reject requests with "
"timestamps older than 5 minutes to prevent replay attacks."
msgstr ""
"Zonder verificatie kan elke partij die uw eindpunt-URL kent vervalste "
"gebeurtenissen verzenden. Lees de ruwe body <em>vóór</em> JSON-parsing, "
"verifieer vervolgens de HMAC-SHA256-ondertekening met uw "
"ondertekeningsgeheim. Lehnen Sie Anfragen mit Zeitstempeln ab, die älter als"
" 5 Minuten sind, um Replay-Angriffe zu verhindern."

#: app/templates/partner/api_docs.html:1004
msgid "Signature format"
msgstr "Ondertekeningsformaat"

#: app/templates/partner/api_docs.html:1006
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"The signed payload is <code class=\"bg-gray-100 px-1 "
"rounded\">{timestamp}.{raw_body}</code> (Unix seconds, a literal dot, then "
"the raw UTF-8 request body). The <code>X-SocietySpeaks-Signature</code> "
"header is <code>sha256=&lt;hex_digest&gt;</code>."
msgstr ""
"De ondertekende payload is <code class=\"bg-gray-100 px-1 "
"rounded\">{timestamp}.{raw_body}</code> (Unix-seconden, een letterlijke "
"punt, gevolgd door de ruwe UTF-8-requestbody). De <code>X-SocietySpeaks-"
"Signature</code>-header is <code>sha256=&lt;hex_digest&gt;</code>."

#: app/templates/partner/api_docs.html:1010
msgid "Verification example"
msgstr "Verificatievoorbeeld"

#: app/templates/partner/api_docs.html:1105
msgid "Manual verification (without the SDK)"
msgstr "Handmatige verificatie (zonder de SDK)"

#: app/templates/partner/api_docs.html:1106
msgid "If you are not using our SDK, follow these steps exactly:"
msgstr "Als u onze SDK niet gebruikt, volgt u deze stappen exact:"

#: app/templates/partner/api_docs.html:1108
msgid "Read the raw request body as bytes — before any JSON parsing."
msgstr "Lees de ruwe requestbody als bytes — vóór eventuele JSON-parsing."

#: app/templates/partner/api_docs.html:1109
msgid ""
"Parse <code>X-SocietySpeaks-Timestamp</code> as an integer. If it is absent "
"or more than 300 seconds in the past, reject with HTTP 400."
msgstr ""
"Parse <code>X-SocietySpeaks-Timestamp</code> als een geheel getal. Indien "
"afwezig of meer dan 300 seconden in het verleden, afwijzen met HTTP 400."

#: app/templates/partner/api_docs.html:1110
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Build the signed payload: <code>{timestamp}</code> + <code>.</code> + raw "
"body bytes."
msgstr ""
"Bouw de ondertekende payload: <code>{timestamp}</code> + <code>.</code> + "
"ruwe body-bytes."

#: app/templates/partner/api_docs.html:1111
msgid ""
"Compute <code>HMAC-SHA256(key=signing_secret, msg=signed_payload)</code> and"
" hex-encode it."
msgstr ""
"Bereken <code>HMAC-SHA256(key=signing_secret, msg=signed_payload)</code> en "
"hex-codeer dit."

#: app/templates/partner/api_docs.html:1112
msgid "Prepend <code>sha256=</code> to form the expected signature string."
msgstr ""
"Voeg <code>sha256=</code> toe om de verwachte ondertekeningsstring te "
"vormen."

#: app/templates/partner/api_docs.html:1113
msgid ""
"Compare with <code>X-SocietySpeaks-Signature</code> using a "
"<strong>constant-time</strong> comparison — <code>hmac.compare_digest</code>"
" in Python, <code>crypto.timingSafeEqual</code> in Node. A plain string "
"equality check leaks timing information."
msgstr ""
"Vergelijk met <code>X-SocietySpeaks-Signature</code> met behulp van een "
"<strong>constant-time</strong>-vergelijking — "
"<code>hmac.compare_digest</code> in Python, "
"<code>crypto.timingSafeEqual</code> in Node. Een eenvoudige string-"
"gelijkheidscontrole lekt timinginformatie."

#: app/templates/partner/api_docs.html:1117
msgid "Secret management"
msgstr "Geheimbeheersing"

#: app/templates/partner/api_docs.html:1119
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"The signing secret is returned once when you create an endpoint — store it "
"securely in an environment variable or secrets manager, never in source "
"code. It is never shown again in the portal. Use <code>POST "
"/api/partner/webhooks/{endpoint_id}/rotate-secret</code> to issue a new "
"secret; briefly accept both the old and new signatures during the rollover "
"period before decommissioning the old one."
msgstr ""
"Het handtekeningsgeheim wordt eenmaal weergegeven wanneer u een eindpunt "
"maakt — bewaar het veilig in een omgevingsvariabele of secrets manager, "
"nooit in broncode. Het wordt nooit opnieuw in het portaal weergegeven. "
"Gebruik <code>POST /api/partner/webhooks/{endpoint_id}/rotate-secret</code> "
"om een nieuw geheim uit te geven; accepteer tijdens de overgangsperiode kort"
" zowel de oude als de nieuwe handtekeningen voordat u de oude buiten bedrijf"
" stelt."

#: app/templates/partner/api_docs.html:1125
msgid "Analytics export (Authenticated)"
msgstr "Analytics-export (Geverifieerd)"

#: app/templates/partner/api_docs.html:1126
msgid "Export usage events in JSON or CSV for BI pipelines."
msgstr "Exporteer gebruiksgebeurtenissen in JSON of CSV voor BI-pijplijnen."

#: app/templates/partner/api_docs.html:1132
msgid ""
"Use <code>format=csv</code> for direct file ingestion, or paginated "
"<code>format=json</code> for API consumers."
msgstr ""
"Gebruik <code>format=csv</code> voor directe bestandsingestie, of "
"gepagineerde <code>format=json</code> voor API-consumers."

#: app/templates/partner/api_docs.html:1137
msgid "Cost and Abuse Protection"
msgstr "Kosten- en misbruikbeveiliging"

#: app/templates/partner/api_docs.html:1140
msgid ""
"<strong>Who pays for what:</strong> Lookup, snapshot, oEmbed, and the embed "
"page do not use our LLM. They are rate-limited per IP (and optional "
"<code>ref</code>) to prevent abuse. <strong>Create Discussion</strong> is "
"the only endpoint that can trigger AI-generated seed statements "
"(OpenAI/Anthropic); it uses <em>our</em> API keys, not yours."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Wie betaalt wat:</strong> Lookup, snapshot, oEmbed en de inbedpagina"
" gebruiken onze LLM niet. Ze zijn beperkt per IP (en optionele "
"<code>ref</code>) om misbruik te voorkomen. <strong>Create "
"Discussion</strong> is het enige eindpunt dat AI-gegenereerde "
"starttaaluitingen kan activeren (OpenAI/Anthropic); het gebruikt "
"<em>onze</em> API-sleutels, niet de jouwe."

#: app/templates/partner/api_docs.html:1143
msgid ""
"<strong>Partners use keys we issue.</strong> Only requests with a valid "
"<code>X-API-Key</code> (from our allowlist) can create discussions. We do "
"not use partner-provided LLM keys for the create flow. If a key is abused, "
"we revoke it."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Partners gebruiken sleutels die wij uitgeven.</strong> Alleen "
"verzoeken met een geldige <code>X-API-Key</code> (van onze allowlist) kunnen"
" discussies maken. We gebruiken geen door partners verstrekte LLM-sleutels "
"voor de creatieve stroom. Als een sleutel wordt misbruikt, trekken we deze "
"in."

#: app/templates/partner/api_docs.html:1146
msgid ""
"<strong>Create Discussion</strong> is limited to <strong>30 requests per "
"hour per API key</strong>. Combined with key control, this caps LLM and "
"database cost from the create endpoint."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Create Discussion</strong> is beperkt tot <strong>30 verzoeken per "
"uur per API-sleutel</strong>. Gecombineerd met sleutelcontrole beperkt dit "
"de LLM- en databasekosten van het creatieve eindpunt."

